quran[9]{c,v,t,f}:
  50,19,"And the stupor of death will come in truth: "
  50,20,"And the Trumpet will be blown - that will be the Day whereof warning (had been given) (i.e. the Day of Resurrection)."
  50,21,"And every person will come forth along with an (angel) to drive (him) and an (angel) to bear witness."
  51,13,"(It will be) a Day when they will be tried (punished i.e. burnt) over the Fire!"
  51,14,""
  51,15,"Verily, the Muttaqûn (the pious. See V.2:2) will be in the midst of Gardens and Springs (in the Paradise),"
  52,4,"And by Al-Bait-ul-Ma‘mûr{1} (the house over the heavens parallel to the Ka‘bah at Makkah, continuously visited by the angels).",footnotes:1:{52:4} See the footnote of {53:12}.
  52,5,"And by the roof raised high (i.e. the heaven)."
  52,6,"And by the sea kept filled (or it will be fire kindled on the Day of Resurrection)."